# Everything under vendor/ MUST be committed. It contains the vendored
# copies of @buhera/purpose, @lavoisier/shapeshifter, and stubs that this
# repo depends on via file:./vendor/... specifiers in package.json. The
# parent .gitignore excludes generic `dist/` directories, and several
# vendored packages ship their built dist/ folder — this file overrides
# those rules for anything inside vendor/.
!*
!**/*
